         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>Θεῷ μεγίστῳ <persName type="divine"><name key="Apollo Ἀπόλλω">Ἀπόλλωνι</name></persName>
               <lb n="2"/>πραηνω <persName><name type="praenomen" key="Marcus Μάρκος">Μάρκος</name> <name type="gentilicium" key="Antonis Αντώνις">Αντώνις</name> <name type="cognomen" key="Silvanus Σιλβανός">Σιλβα
               <lb n="3" break="no"/>νός</name></persName>, λεγιῶνος <num type="ordinal" value="22">ΚΒ</num> ευχήν ἀνέθηκεν.
            </ab></div>
         
         <div type="translation">
            <p>Markos Antonis Silvanos of the 22nd legion dedicated [this plaque in fulfillment of a] vow to the greatest of the gods, Apollo of gentle mind.</p></div>
         
